  "body": "# Feature Issue\r\n\r\n### User Story\r\n\r\n>As a user\r\n>I want to be able to distinguish between read and unread notifications\r\n>So that I know which ones require my attention\r\n\r\n### Design\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/46027/192865009-efed41d8-5f88-4261-886a-112ec7ee95eb.png\" width=\"800\" />\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\nThis feature is part of a larger effort to create a new Activity Center. Please, reach out to members of the UX team before starting this work in case there are important details not apparent in Figma.\r\n\r\n- [Figma - Activity Center user journeys](https://www.figma.com/file/eDfxTa9IoaCMUy5cLTp0ys/Shell-for-Mobile?node-id=639%3A21926)\r\n",
